			BOSS The Scent Intense
		


Intimately reflecting the story of seduction, BOSS The Scent Intense parfums are a pair of unforgettable fragrances for the BOSS man and woman. With high oil concentrations, aphrodisiac notes and exotic ingredients, each is an irresistible combination with the power to captivate the senses.









